# sarani108.adesha — 108-multiplication table: punaH + gaNaya
# Step 1: count to 108 via punaH
sthApaya tAla 0
punaH 108 sthApaya tAla tAla + 1
# Step 2: gaNaya shows multiples 1x through 9x
gaNaya tAla * 1
gaNaya tAla * 2
gaNaya tAla * 3
gaNaya tAla * 4
gaNaya tAla * 5
gaNaya tAla * 6
gaNaya tAla * 7
gaNaya tAla * 8
gaNaya tAla * 9
